::Cygnar::
       He glances between Empath and Galvatron.  He sighs and turns to face 
Empath.  "Stay out of my mind.  Or it will be most unpleasant for you.  
Okay?"  He winks condescendingly.  He concentrates solely on hatred for her 
and mumbles something about bloody telepaths.
